metadata.name: AI Generative Art 1
metadata.description:
Title: AI Generative Art  
Artist: Godwits  
Year: 2023  
Smart Contract By: Manifold  
Artist Royalty: 7.5%  

"AI Generative Art Collection" uses artificial intelligence to explore the boundary between design and art. Created through the use of machine learning algorithms and other AI technologies, each piece in this collection was born using custom datasets of various elements to offer a unique collaborative work.  

Each series in this collection will have anywhere from 25 to 100 experimental works by Godwits. Series are under the properties sub-category.  

Limited to personal non-commercial use and resale rights of NFT are granted.  
All other terms & rights are reserved to Abstract Art Labs LLC
